## 4. Information Architecture

```
Web App
├── / — Plan Selector (home screen)
│   ├── Create new plan → /plans/[planId]/personal-info
│   └── Import backup (.json)
└── /plans/[planId]/
    ├── (index) — Per-plan home (progress, section list, continue bar)
    ├── personal-info
    ├── epa
    ├── care-contacts
    ├── will
    ├── personal-wishes
    ├── end-of-life
    ├── body-care
    ├── organ-donation
    ├── treatment-preferences
    ├── signature
    └── export
```

Each `/plans/[planId]/*` route is wrapped in a `PlanProvider` layout that loads and saves the correct plan by UUID. `params` is unwrapped with `React.use()` (Next.js 15 requirement before accessing `params.planId`).

